<NAME_MOB_KENNETH>
You lookin' to buy something? Talk to me from
the front o' the counter, if ya'd please.

<NAME_MOB_KENNETH>
How's tricks? Things are lookin' up, 'round these
parts. Hope the same's true for you!

<NAME_MOB_KENNETH>
If you're shippin', I'm buyin'. Just say the word!
